Title: Gauge Consistent Wilson Renormalization Group I: Abelian Case
Authors: Michele Simionato
Comments: Latex2e, 39 pages, 3 eps figures. Revised version to appear in Int.
  J. Mod. Phys
Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A15 (2000) 2121-2152
\\
  A version of the Wilson Renormalization Group Equation consistent with gauge
symmetry is presented. A perturbative renormalizability proof is established. A
wilsonian derivation of the Callan-Symanzik equation is given.
